
  - ------ - ------- - ------- - -- --------- ----- 
   The Master
  - ------ - ------- - ------- - -- --------- -----

  The Master is designated by the Magi to be the operating
  mortal of the guild;  Much power is given to the Master
  to exercise in what he believes to be the Will.
  The Master's duties include overseeing the overall
  running and performance of the Servants, and it is
  often at the Master's hand at which a Traitor will
  pay the eternal price of death.

         MASTER: Unknown

